          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1707820911180-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> in half</p><p>Slice your<strong> chestnut mushrooms</strong> finely</p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Remove the <strong>homemade beans</strong> from the heat and set aside for later</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1707820852125-x200.jpg",
