    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan with the tomato halves to a medium-low heat and add another knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into the pan</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 2-3 min or until the tomato has softened and the egg is done to your liking</p><p>Tip: Give your egg a little shake before you crack for a perfectly centred yolk!</p>",
